<para><bold>Doxygen Awesome</bold> is a custom <bold>CSS theme for Doxygen HTML-documentation</bold> with lots of customization parameters.</para>
<sect1 id="md_doxygen_awesome_css__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md24">
<title>Motivation</title>
<para>I really like how the Doxygen HTML-documentation is structured! But IMHO it looks a bit outdated.</para>
<para>This theme is an attempt to update the visuals of Doxygen without changing its overall layout too much.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="md_doxygen_awesome_css__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md25">
